  "detailed_description": "Discover the quiet dystopia of Fortune's Run, where food is free yet people starve and every living soul on New Zabra is bought and paid for by off-world interests. A classic FPS with undertones of role-playing in the spirit of Deus Ex and EYE: Divine Cybermancy, featuring the campy tone of space operas and titles like Metal Gear Solid.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1692240/extras/9a10face2161fab13fdf7bf6b8b36a5b.poster.avif?t=1724977565\" width=576 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1692240/extras/9a10face2161fab13fdf7bf6b8b36a5b.webm?t=1724977565\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1692240/extras/9a10face2161fab13fdf7bf6b8b36a5b.mp4?t=1724977565\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Master an innovative combat system inspired by fighting games and character action titles. Memorize combos and specials that break stance, use grabs and mix-ups to throw off your enemies' guard. The depth will keep you practicing for months.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1692240/extras/4dfd04f9ea189b372a0c01bb8067bf0b.poster.avif?t=1724977565\" width=576 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1692240/extras/4dfd04f9ea189b372a0c01bb8067bf0b.webm?t=1724977565\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1692240/extras/4dfd04f9ea189b372a0c01bb8067bf0b.mp4?t=1724977565\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Lose yourself in a post-industrial world of barren factories and boarded up store-fronts. Explore immersive environments, meet eclectic low-lives and witness Mozah's tragic tale in full voice-acted glory.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1692240/extras/c3d8d1df303a017bc63235517d955fd3.poster.avif?t=1724977565\" width=576 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1692240/extras/c3d8d1df303a017bc63235517d955fd3.webm?t=1724977565\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1692240/extras/c3d8d1df303a017bc63235517d955fd3.mp4?t=1724977565\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Learn to defend yourself with invincibility frames, parries, counters and true Quake-engine strafe-jumping movement. Damage is lethal, combat is tactical and practice is imperative. A return to the form of old classics on maximum difficulty. Blink and you're dead!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1692240/extras/ded395629b39b149f710c55d24db883a.poster.avif?t=1724977565\" width=576 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1692240/extras/ded395629b39b149f710c55d24db883a.webm?t=1724977565\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1692240/extras/ded395629b39b149f710c55d24db883a.mp4?t=1724977565\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Travel to distant stars and lay eyes on set-pieces inspired by the science-fiction greats. A fully simulated centrifugal space station, a train that rides up a cable to the heavens. No two levels the same, always with something to impress.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1692240/extras/6b93dd60d04b2bfe276d0fe257e39e16.poster.avif?t=1724977565\" width=576 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1692240/extras/6b93dd60d04b2bfe276d0fe257e39e16.webm?t=1724977565\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1692240/extras/6b93dd60d04b2bfe276d0fe257e39e16.mp4?t=1724977565\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Embrace the pain. The only way to survive is to learn, and the only way to learn is to fail. With a deeply customizable difficulty system and endless mechanics to master, Fortune's Run will leave you only two options: persistence or death!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1692240/extras/9ac5434568481261aa4927589f09ecc4.avif?t=1724977565\" width=300 height=312 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Discover the quiet dystopia of Fortune's Run, where food is free yet people starve and every living soul on New Zabra is bought and paid for by off-world interests. A classic FPS with undertones of role-playing in the spirit of Deus Ex and EYE: Divine Cybermancy, featuring the campy tone of space operas and titles like Metal Gear Solid.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1692240/extras/9a10face2161fab13fdf7bf6b8b36a5b.poster.avif?t=1724977565\" width=576 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1692240/extras/9a10face2161fab13fdf7bf6b8b36a5b.webm?t=1724977565\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1692240/extras/9a10face2161fab13fdf7bf6b8b36a5b.mp4?t=1724977565\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Master an innovative combat system inspired by fighting games and character action titles. Memorize combos and specials that break stance, use grabs and mix-ups to throw off your enemies' guard. The depth will keep you practicing for months.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1692240/extras/4dfd04f9ea189b372a0c01bb8067bf0b.poster.avif?t=1724977565\" width=576 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1692240/extras/4dfd04f9ea189b372a0c01bb8067bf0b.webm?t=1724977565\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1692240/extras/4dfd04f9ea189b372a0c01bb8067bf0b.mp4?t=1724977565\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Lose yourself in a post-industrial world of barren factories and boarded up store-fronts. Explore immersive environments, meet eclectic low-lives and witness Mozah's tragic tale in full voice-acted glory.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1692240/extras/c3d8d1df303a017bc63235517d955fd3.poster.avif?t=1724977565\" width=576 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1692240/extras/c3d8d1df303a017bc63235517d955fd3.webm?t=1724977565\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1692240/extras/c3d8d1df303a017bc63235517d955fd3.mp4?t=1724977565\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Learn to defend yourself with invincibility frames, parries, counters and true Quake-engine strafe-jumping movement. Damage is lethal, combat is tactical and practice is imperative. A return to the form of old classics on maximum difficulty. Blink and you're dead!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1692240/extras/ded395629b39b149f710c55d24db883a.poster.avif?t=1724977565\" width=576 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1692240/extras/ded395629b39b149f710c55d24db883a.webm?t=1724977565\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1692240/extras/ded395629b39b149f710c55d24db883a.mp4?t=1724977565\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Travel to distant stars and lay eyes on set-pieces inspired by the science-fiction greats. A fully simulated centrifugal space station, a train that rides up a cable to the heavens. No two levels the same, always with something to impress.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1692240/extras/6b93dd60d04b2bfe276d0fe257e39e16.poster.avif?t=1724977565\" width=576 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1692240/extras/6b93dd60d04b2bfe276d0fe257e39e16.webm?t=1724977565\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1692240/extras/6b93dd60d04b2bfe276d0fe257e39e16.mp4?t=1724977565\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Embrace the pain. The only way to survive is to learn, and the only way to learn is to fail. With a deeply customizable difficulty system and endless mechanics to master, Fortune's Run will leave you only two options: persistence or death!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1692240/extras/9ac5434568481261aa4927589f09ecc4.avif?t=1724977565\" width=300 height=312 /></span>",
